  <brief_title>Oxaliplatin With Gemcitabine in Patients With Carcinoma of the Urothelial Tract</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Monocentric Study of Oxaliplatin in Combination With Gemcitabine in Patients With Advanced/Metastatic Transitional Cell Carcinoma of the Urothelial Tract</official_title>
  <sponsors>
