  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a phase II monocentric study of oxaliplatin (Ox) in combination with gemcitabine
      (Gem; GEMOX) in patients (pts) with advanced/metastatic transitional cell carcinoma (TCC) of
      the urothelial tract.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
